<HEADLINE>
<P>
PALM LATITUDES: VERBATIM 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 Excerpts from a press release for Amirage de Givenchy bath products:  
</P>
<P>
 First Stage: Purity.Innocence, tenderness, a caress: DELICATE PERFUMED SOAP 
rolls over the skin and slides between the fingers in a light lather. A playful 
and deliciously emollient round pebble, which leaves us with its exquisite 
aura. 
</P>
<P>
 Second Stage: Freshness. Protection, confidence, ease: the new roll-on called 
PERFUMED FRESHNESS is an alcohol-free deodorant, an emulsion of pure softness 
and real safety. . . . 
</P>
<P>
 Fifth Stage: Sophistication. Gentleness, fluidity, lightness: . . . talc is 
the skin's icing sugar, a butterfly kiss planted in the body's most secret 
folds. The rapture of PERFUME TALC . . . . 
</P>
<P>
 And here we thought we were just getting ready for work.  
