</P>
<P>
 The 39 Steps Bravo, Tuesday, 5 and 9:30 p.m.; Saturday, 7:30 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 Tunes of Glory Bravo, Wednesday, 9:30 a.m. and 3 p.m. 
</P>
<P>
 Public Enemy TMC, Saturday, 5:25 a.m. Kevin Thomas 
