</BYLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 A Palestinian woman was shot and killed Saturday when Israeli troops fired on 
stone throwers in the West Bank town of Ramallah, hospital officials said. 
</P>
<P>
 Soham Murshed Suwaiti, 37, apparently was sitting in a car when she was shot 
