<DOCNO> LA061294-0352 </DOCNO>
<DOCID> 050843 </DOCID>
<SOURCE>
<P>
 Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</SOURCE>
<DATE>
<P>
June 12, 1994, Sunday, Home Edition 
</P>
</DATE>
<SECTION>
<P>
Business; Part D; Page 1; Column 3; Financial Desk 
</P>
