 West Germany 1 
</P>
<P>
 July 11 at Madrid 
</P>
<P>
 Italy recovered from missing an early penalty kick to outplay West Germany in 
the second half. Paolo Rossi, Marco Tardelli and Sandro Altobelli scored for 
the skillful Italians, while Paul Breitner scored West Germany's only goal. It 
was Italy's third World Cup triumph. 
</P>
<P>
