<HEADLINE>
<P>
WORLD CUP '94; WORLD CUP / USA 1994; ROAD TO THE FINALS; THE QUALIFYING GROUPS 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
 It took more than two years of qualifying matches for 22 national teams, of 
140 entries, to earn a berth in the World Cup finals. The United States, as 
host, and Germany, as defending champion, qualified automatically, rounding out 
the 24-team field. Here is how the teams qualified: 
</P>
