Costacurta Defender 5 Paolo Maldini Defender 6 Franco Baresi Defender 7 Lorenzo 
Minotti Defender 8 Roberto Mussi Defender 9 Mauro Tassotti Defender 11 Demetrio 
Albertini Midfielder 13 Dino Baggio Midfielder 14 Nicola Berti Midfielder 15 
Antonio Conte Midfielder 16 Roberto Donadoni Midfielder 17 Alberigo Evani 
Midfielder 10 Roberto Baggio Forward 18 Pierluigi Casiraghi Forward 19 Daniele 
Massaro Forward 20 Giuseppe Signori Forward 21 Gianfranco Zola Forward Grahame 
L. Jones 
</P>
